WEBVTT

00:38.937 --> 00:40.421
[♪ adventurous music plays]

00:40.421 --> 00:40.521
[♪ adventurous music plays]

00:48.937 --> 00:49.937
[Lo'ak] Come on, Bro.

00:51.021 --> 00:52.021
[laughs]

00:53.062 --> 00:55.979
Whoo! Whoo, whoo, whoo!

00:56.646 --> 00:57.562
[chuckles]

01:05.104 --> 01:06.729
Whoo! [chuckles]

01:07.479 --> 01:08.854
[Lo'ak ululates]

01:10.812 --> 01:12.021
Whoo!

01:12.104 --> 01:13.854
Whoa. Whoa.

01:13.937 --> 01:14.937
Hey, watch it.

01:15.021 --> 01:16.771
You were in my way, Bro.

01:16.854 --> 01:18.354
Oh, okay.

01:24.396 --> 01:25.604
Whoo!

01:26.937 --> 01:27.771
[grunts]

01:29.604 --> 01:30.812
Whoo!

01:32.479 --> 01:33.979
Whoo!

01:35.521 --> 01:37.646
You want to go faster, huh?

01:45.604 --> 01:47.687
[chuckles] Whoo-hoo!

01:54.146 --> 01:55.479
That was cool, Bro.

01:56.146 --> 01:57.729
[chuckles]<c.s0> Skxawng

02:02.354 --> 02:03.646
High four.

02:04.229 --> 02:05.229
[sighs]

02:09.687 --> 02:11.896
[sighs]

02:14.479 --> 02:15.729
Little Brother,

02:20.979 --> 02:22.187
How did I die?

02:28.854 --> 02:30.312
You got shot.

02:35.229 --> 02:36.562
Then we had to go back.

02:37.354 --> 02:38.354
That's not your fault.

02:38.437 --> 02:39.604
Tell that to Dad.

02:46.604 --> 02:48.396
That's just you, Little Bro.

02:58.812 --> 03:00.187
I love you, Brother.

03:00.812 --> 03:01.812
<c.s0>Skxawng.

03:07.729 --> 03:09.312
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>I killed my brother.

03:10.187 --> 03:11.396
<c.s0>No matter what happens,

03:12.146 --> 03:15.521
<c.s0>I have to live with that
for the rest of my life.

03:44.687 --> 03:47.646
[panting]

03:54.021 --> 03:55.104
I wish I could do it.

03:55.646 --> 03:57.687
No, I wish I could do it.

04:02.062 --> 04:03.062
Yeah,

04:04.979 --> 04:07.229
[imitates choking]

04:10.271 --> 04:11.396
Hey, watch the stitches.

04:21.021 --> 04:23.771
[♪ Neytiri singing in Na'vi]

04:38.271 --> 04:39.854
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>The fire of hate

04:39.937 --> 04:41.812
<c.s0>leaves only
the ash of grief.

04:43.771 --> 04:45.104
<c.s0>My mother mourned

04:45.187 --> 04:46.271
<c.s0>the ancient way,

04:46.812 --> 04:49.354
<c.s0>singing her son's life
during the daily eclipse.

04:51.271 --> 04:53.146
<c.s0>Because the light
always returns.

04:59.854 --> 05:00.771
[singing fades]

05:02.687 --> 05:03.812
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>There's the   way,

05:04.812 --> 05:06.312
<c.s0>and then there's
my dad's way.

05:07.021 --> 05:09.396
<c.s0>Say nothing.
Keep busy.

05:10.937 --> 05:14.104
[breathes heavily]

05:24.604 --> 05:25.604
[ilu shrieks]

05:28.229 --> 05:30.479
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>The Reef People say
the sea washes you clean.

05:31.979 --> 05:33.479
<c.s0>Washes away your sins.

05:33.562 --> 05:34.729
[ilu squeaks]

06:10.521 --> 06:11.521
What do you got?

06:14.771 --> 06:16.229
That thing's useless.

06:16.812 --> 06:17.937
Focus, boy.

06:34.354 --> 06:35.271
Hey, excuse me.

06:45.104 --> 06:46.104
Bro.

06:47.729 --> 06:48.979
Ah, sick.

06:50.396 --> 06:51.396
What is this?

06:52.646 --> 06:53.646
Tsireya?

06:55.146 --> 06:56.479
What are you doing?

06:58.854 --> 07:01.312
This is an AR, all right?

07:03.521 --> 07:04.687
Empty.

07:05.604 --> 07:06.604
Slap it.

07:07.562 --> 07:08.521
Rack it.

07:08.604 --> 07:09.896
And then, boom,

07:09.979 --> 07:11.021
you can just spray.

07:13.354 --> 07:15.437
See? Ceramic action.

07:17.646 --> 07:19.646
This is not the <c.s0>Na'vi

07:19.729 --> 07:20.854
<c.s0>Jakesully

07:23.104 --> 07:24.104
You know this.

07:24.187 --> 07:25.187
To touch them

07:25.271 --> 07:26.687
poisons the heart.

07:27.187 --> 07:28.187
Eywa

07:28.271 --> 07:29.354
will provide.

07:29.979 --> 07:31.854
[sighs] Right.

07:35.271 --> 07:36.104
Tuk.

07:37.646 --> 07:39.354
not gathering these things.

07:39.437 --> 07:40.937
Your woman

07:41.021 --> 07:42.146
needs you.

07:48.062 --> 07:49.604
This is our home.

07:49.687 --> 07:51.562
I said I would stand and fight,

07:54.437 --> 07:56.271
We sank the demon ship.

07:56.354 --> 07:58.104
The pink skins fear us now.

07:59.729 --> 08:01.687
Yeah? We got lucky.

08:01.771 --> 08:03.229
And they got many more ships.

08:04.021 --> 08:05.437
Least we got these.

08:06.646 --> 08:08.979
Jakesully

08:09.646 --> 08:10.979
It is not guns we need.

08:11.062 --> 08:12.479
It is Rider of Last Shadow.

08:14.271 --> 08:15.896
Ride great <c.s0>toruk

08:15.979 --> 08:18.021
as you did before.

08:22.687 --> 08:24.021
you become the beast.

08:29.062 --> 08:30.937
I will not become

08:31.021 --> 08:32.979
<c.s0>Toruk Makto

08:34.021 --> 08:35.229
<c.s0>Jakesully

08:36.187 --> 08:38.312
you are always <c.s0>Toruk Makto.

08:39.479 --> 08:41.521
Come. Rotxo.

08:47.187 --> 08:48.229
<c.s0>Can you hear me?

08:50.146 --> 08:51.146
Go on, Doc.

08:52.062 --> 08:55.312
<c.s0>So, uh, we've been through
the wreck, inside and out.

08:55.396 --> 08:58.562
<c.s0>Uh, we've searched to about
a 200-meter radius around it.

08:59.104 --> 09:00.604
<c.s0>We didn't find
any bodies.

09:00.687 --> 09:03.687
<c.s0>Just crew or...
what's left of 'em.

09:03.771 --> 09:06.062
Well, keep looking, Doctor.

09:06.146 --> 09:08.354
Roger that.

09:08.437 --> 09:09.271
<c.s0>Of note though,

09:09.354 --> 09:11.354
<c.s0>I did find an interesting
new algae.

09:13.146 --> 09:14.562
<c.s0>Hello? Can you hear me?

09:19.104 --> 09:21.562
Nope. He made it out.

09:26.687 --> 09:27.771
I gave you a ship.

09:30.354 --> 09:31.771
Yeah. Along with my crew.

09:32.604 --> 09:33.604
All dead.

09:34.604 --> 09:36.354
You brought me out here,

09:36.437 --> 09:38.479
twenty-six trillion miles,

09:38.562 --> 09:40.187
for a single mission,

09:40.271 --> 09:41.771
a kinetic hard kill op

09:41.854 --> 09:43.854
against one guy.

09:44.396 --> 09:46.312
I ain't backing off.

09:49.979 --> 09:52.062
Are we still connected? Hello?

09:53.187 --> 09:54.771
<c.s0>Do they have me on mute?

10:06.521 --> 10:07.729
It was our strength.

10:15.062 --> 10:16.062
No!

10:17.312 --> 10:18.396
It's ruined!

10:19.604 --> 10:21.604
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>Everything I touch
gets ruined.

10:26.729 --> 10:28.229
<c.s0>They never talked about it.

10:30.271 --> 10:31.729
<c.s0>But it was there
in the room.

10:32.354 --> 10:34.229
<c.s0>Like a crouching thanator.

10:34.312 --> 10:35.562
[sighs]

10:41.604 --> 10:42.604
So...

10:52.729 --> 10:54.687
[sighs]

10:54.771 --> 10:57.187
[breathing shakily]

11:08.021 --> 11:10.187
So, you agree with Ronal?

11:15.937 --> 11:17.437
in front of that woman.

11:20.062 --> 11:21.271
Look, I'm a marine.

11:27.312 --> 11:28.437
Or a prayer. [scoffs]

11:36.854 --> 11:37.854
Oh, that's right.

11:43.396 --> 11:44.396
Jake!

11:59.812 --> 12:00.937
All I have...

12:02.229 --> 12:03.479
is my faith

12:07.229 --> 12:09.604
[breathing shakily]

12:09.687 --> 12:11.271
You have this family.

12:25.479 --> 12:26.812
And you have me.

12:29.104 --> 12:31.062
And I love you so much.

12:35.562 --> 12:37.979
[sobs]

12:40.687 --> 12:43.979
[chittering]

12:44.062 --> 12:45.729
[♪ adventurous music plays]

12:45.812 --> 12:46.937
[bellows]

12:52.854 --> 12:54.479
[whistles]

12:56.687 --> 12:59.021
[rumbles]

13:03.479 --> 13:05.521
[tulkun vocalizing]

13:23.937 --> 13:24.937
Whoa. Bro, Bro.

13:25.521 --> 13:26.521
[exclaims]

13:28.187 --> 13:30.687
This is sick! [laughs]

13:36.979 --> 13:38.479
Whoo!

13:54.646 --> 13:56.229
That was insane, cuz.

13:56.312 --> 13:57.479
I know, right, Bro?

13:58.521 --> 13:59.562
[Tsireya laughs]

13:59.646 --> 14:00.812
I thought you were dead.

14:01.562 --> 14:03.687
[both imitate splash, laugh]

14:11.062 --> 14:13.062
but by the <c.s0>tulkun

14:13.146 --> 14:14.062
[Payakan rumbling]

14:16.479 --> 14:17.854
He bears those deaths.

14:20.021 --> 14:22.812
I'm sorry. You saved us all.

14:23.437 --> 14:24.812
[rumbling]

14:29.479 --> 14:31.229
[distorted] Forever, Brother.

14:31.312 --> 14:32.312
[normal] Always.

14:32.396 --> 14:34.187
[bellows]

14:38.104 --> 14:41.062
[exo-pack beeping]

14:41.896 --> 14:43.729
[gasping, choking]

14:45.354 --> 14:46.354
Dad!

14:52.312 --> 14:53.562
Hey! Wake up! Where is it?

15:08.521 --> 15:09.854
[beeping stops]

15:11.396 --> 15:13.104
Spider, no.

15:13.187 --> 15:14.187
Breathe.

15:16.271 --> 15:17.646
[Jake] Deep and slow.

15:18.312 --> 15:19.479
Deep and slow.

15:26.687 --> 15:28.812
<c.s0>Skxawng.

15:29.354 --> 15:30.896
skxawng.

15:32.521 --> 15:33.521
Pay attention.

15:37.479 --> 15:39.479
-Skxawng

15:41.812 --> 15:43.062
[horn blowing]

15:43.979 --> 15:45.021
[Tsireya] The Windtraders.

15:49.729 --> 15:50.729
Come on!

15:50.812 --> 15:51.937
Come on. Let's go.

15:54.604 --> 15:55.646
Come on, Tuk.

15:55.729 --> 15:58.229
[♪ joyful music plays]

15:59.521 --> 16:01.146
[Lo'ak] Whoo!

16:05.187 --> 16:06.187
[whoops]

16:14.146 --> 16:15.604
[whoops]

16:18.062 --> 16:20.354
Hey! [whooping]

16:35.687 --> 16:36.687
Tsireya.

16:37.521 --> 16:38.896
[gasps]

16:40.354 --> 16:41.979
Look. [chuckles]

16:42.062 --> 16:43.604
Look at him.

16:45.979 --> 16:47.479
As long as he's no trouble.

16:53.687 --> 16:54.729
[Jake] Please, sit.

17:02.354 --> 17:03.979
[sighs]

17:12.354 --> 17:13.354
day and night.

17:25.687 --> 17:26.687
[Jake] It's too dangerous.

17:31.271 --> 17:32.104
Mom.

17:41.562 --> 17:42.562
It's Spider.

17:43.437 --> 17:44.646
Please, Jake.

17:46.896 --> 17:48.021
Dad, this isn't right.

17:48.104 --> 17:50.229
Spider is part of this family.

17:50.312 --> 17:51.729
He will never

17:54.437 --> 17:55.646
[Kiri sobs]

18:06.062 --> 18:07.187
All right?

18:07.271 --> 18:08.271
I hate you!

18:10.646 --> 18:11.979
Don't touch me!

18:18.437 --> 18:20.021
I already lost my brother.

18:20.729 --> 18:22.229
I can't lose anyone else.

18:24.146 --> 18:25.146
[hisses]

18:28.812 --> 18:30.479
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>Sullys stick together.

18:30.562 --> 18:32.104
[Jake sighs]

18:32.187 --> 18:34.396
[Lo'ak]<c.s0> Yep, that's
the family motto.

18:39.979 --> 18:41.604
[Jake] Okay, okay.

18:45.687 --> 18:46.521
Kiri.

18:58.396 --> 19:00.104
Yeah. Cool.

19:03.146 --> 19:04.604
[shrieks]

19:12.937 --> 19:14.104
[Jake] Hey, stay here.

19:20.312 --> 19:21.854
We won't be any trouble.

19:21.937 --> 19:23.312
You are already trouble.

19:23.396 --> 19:25.396
A trader must move freely.

19:25.479 --> 19:26.479
We cannot choose sides.

19:27.312 --> 19:29.062
Having <c.s0>Toruk Makto

19:32.979 --> 19:34.646
Yeah, but you're mistaken.

19:34.729 --> 19:36.812
<c.s0>Toruk Makto

19:45.771 --> 19:47.187
and protect your caravan.

19:50.229 --> 19:51.354
Perhaps so.

19:52.312 --> 19:54.604
The <c.s0>Mangkwan

19:55.104 --> 19:56.104
[Jake] Hmm.

20:00.937 --> 20:02.146
[sighs]

20:05.312 --> 20:06.687
Cast off!

20:07.979 --> 20:09.021
Come on.

20:09.104 --> 20:10.396
Cast off!

20:12.562 --> 20:14.229
Cast off below!

20:16.937 --> 20:18.854
[♪ singing in Na'vi]

20:19.729 --> 20:21.771
Lo'ak! [chuckles] Lo'ak!

20:23.896 --> 20:24.729
Lo'ak! [chuckles]

20:26.146 --> 20:27.479
Ready about!

20:31.479 --> 20:32.979
[Peylak] Bow to starboard.

20:40.521 --> 20:42.854
Windward vanes out full!

20:45.229 --> 20:46.354
[crew members] Heave!

20:46.937 --> 20:48.271
Heave!

20:48.354 --> 20:49.687
Heave!

20:52.479 --> 20:53.729
Heave!

20:55.979 --> 20:58.229
Lighten ship. Come up easy.

21:05.854 --> 21:07.396
Windward out full!

21:08.854 --> 21:10.812
[chuckles]

21:11.312 --> 21:13.812
Make all and set taut!

21:54.771 --> 21:56.187
Whoo! Yeah!

22:03.354 --> 22:05.229
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>Everyone mourns
in their own way.

22:09.229 --> 22:10.396
<c.s0>For me,

22:10.937 --> 22:12.229
<c.s0>it's being up here alone.

22:15.104 --> 22:16.854
<c.s0>I feel him with me.

22:19.354 --> 22:20.479
Bro, check it out.

22:21.104 --> 22:23.396
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>I hear his voice
in the wind.

22:24.937 --> 22:26.437
[ululates]

22:35.396 --> 22:36.646
[squawks]

22:36.729 --> 22:37.854
[Jake sighs]

22:39.562 --> 22:40.562
Hold this.

22:52.312 --> 22:53.729
I should carry a rifle.

22:53.812 --> 22:55.146
And I could fly with you.

22:55.229 --> 22:56.229
Yeah.

22:57.062 --> 22:58.479
That's gonna happen. [grunts]

22:58.562 --> 23:00.021
Why not?

23:01.687 --> 23:03.187
I know what I'm doing.

23:03.729 --> 23:05.187
Yeah? Where's your comms?

23:05.271 --> 23:06.687
I called you like five times.

23:08.354 --> 23:09.979
Wear your comms.

23:10.687 --> 23:11.687
That's rule number one.

23:13.646 --> 23:14.979
You can't even do that.

23:21.229 --> 23:22.479
[groans]

23:30.354 --> 23:31.354
That's it.

23:33.979 --> 23:35.062
What you got?

23:42.812 --> 23:44.021
A routine flyby.

23:44.771 --> 23:45.979
Here's the enhanced.

23:50.437 --> 23:51.646
Smile, bitches.

23:56.354 --> 23:57.354
I got coordinates.

23:57.437 --> 23:58.687
Let's mount up.

24:00.021 --> 24:01.062
Thank you.

24:09.687 --> 24:11.979
[horn blowing]

24:15.854 --> 24:17.812
Haul in hard!

24:17.896 --> 24:19.479
Haul in hard!

24:27.187 --> 24:28.771
Steady on course.

24:31.146 --> 24:33.146
[exo-pack beeping]

24:34.021 --> 24:35.021
[beeping stops]

24:35.104 --> 24:36.104
Your pack.

24:49.771 --> 24:50.771
Clear ahead.

25:06.771 --> 25:07.896
Jake!

25:07.979 --> 25:09.271
<c.s0>Mangkwan!

25:09.354 --> 25:10.687
[♪ suspenseful music plays]

25:10.771 --> 25:11.812
<c.s0>Mangkwan

25:11.896 --> 25:12.979
Sound the alarm!

25:14.521 --> 25:15.646
[shouts]

25:18.604 --> 25:19.437
[ululating]

25:22.437 --> 25:23.646
Get these out.

25:26.937 --> 25:28.146
[grunts]

25:28.771 --> 25:29.771
[shouts]

25:30.771 --> 25:32.104
[shrieks]

25:34.604 --> 25:35.479
[grunts]

25:36.146 --> 25:37.062
Go, go.

25:43.771 --> 25:45.646
[Jake shouts]

25:49.021 --> 25:50.437
[shouts]

25:57.771 --> 25:59.479
[panting]

26:02.979 --> 26:04.396
[shrieks]

26:09.187 --> 26:10.479
Spider, here.

26:14.437 --> 26:15.521
Shit, my comms.

26:24.354 --> 26:25.187
[grunts]

26:28.646 --> 26:29.729
Stay with the girls. [coughs]

26:36.896 --> 26:38.062
[shrieks]

26:43.396 --> 26:44.437
[grunts]

26:45.354 --> 26:46.187
[shrieks]

26:48.687 --> 26:49.854
[shrieks]

26:52.104 --> 26:53.104
[shouts]

27:00.896 --> 27:01.937
[shouts]

27:04.021 --> 27:05.021
Come on.

27:06.729 --> 27:07.771
Release.

27:09.437 --> 27:10.854
[grunting]

27:13.187 --> 27:14.646
[pants]

27:14.729 --> 27:16.062
[shrieks]

27:16.146 --> 27:17.812
[breathing heavily]

27:17.896 --> 27:19.187
[ululates]

27:19.271 --> 27:20.396
[Spider] Get back.

27:24.687 --> 27:25.687
[shouts]

27:28.312 --> 27:30.062
[groaning]

27:34.479 --> 27:35.604
[groans]

27:36.396 --> 27:37.312
[shouts]

27:37.396 --> 27:38.687
[grunting]

27:39.271 --> 27:40.771
[both grunting]

27:41.271 --> 27:42.646
[panting]

27:53.604 --> 27:54.604
[grunts, shouts]

27:54.687 --> 27:55.771
[grunts]

27:57.729 --> 27:58.646
[shrieks]

28:04.437 --> 28:05.937
[grunts, exhales sharply]

28:06.896 --> 28:07.729
[shouts]

28:08.854 --> 28:09.854
I am

28:09.937 --> 28:11.229
the fire!

28:11.812 --> 28:14.146
[shouting]

28:15.021 --> 28:16.437
[snarls]

28:23.354 --> 28:25.104
[shouts]

28:25.187 --> 28:26.396
[grunts]

28:28.771 --> 28:30.062
[shouting]

28:30.146 --> 28:31.146
Oh, sh...

28:33.437 --> 28:34.437
[grunts]

28:35.729 --> 28:36.729
Hey!

28:37.271 --> 28:38.271
[groans]

28:39.062 --> 28:40.229
[shouts]

28:40.312 --> 28:41.437
[grunts]

28:47.021 --> 28:48.229
[shouts]

28:48.312 --> 28:49.687
[shouts]

28:49.771 --> 28:51.646
[groans]

28:53.062 --> 28:54.062
[shouts]

28:55.396 --> 28:56.979
[groans, shouts]

29:00.104 --> 29:01.437
[shrieks]

29:05.104 --> 29:06.812
[both grunting]

29:09.521 --> 29:10.771
[grunts, shouts]

29:16.354 --> 29:17.687
Climb. Climb.

29:17.771 --> 29:19.229
Get up. Hurry.

29:20.979 --> 29:22.021
[exclaims]

29:22.687 --> 29:23.854
[shrieks]

29:27.687 --> 29:28.687
Come on, let's go.

29:28.771 --> 29:29.687
Hold on.

29:34.937 --> 29:35.854
[grunts]

29:36.729 --> 29:37.562
[grunts]

29:37.646 --> 29:39.187
[♪ dramatic music plays]

29:42.646 --> 29:43.521
[scoffs]

29:43.604 --> 29:45.354
[gasping]

30:01.729 --> 30:03.604
[screeching]

30:14.104 --> 30:15.354
Lo'ak.

30:16.812 --> 30:17.812
Now!

30:17.896 --> 30:19.562
[grunts] Go, go, go, go, go.

30:19.646 --> 30:20.646
Hold on, everyone.

30:23.396 --> 30:25.479
[shouting, grunting]

30:33.521 --> 30:34.687
Hold on, Lo'ak.

30:34.771 --> 30:36.187
[shrieks, shouts]

30:38.521 --> 30:40.021
[Tuk, Kiri scream]

30:42.687 --> 30:44.812
[grunting]

30:45.521 --> 30:48.229
[grunts] Hold on. Tuk!

30:50.729 --> 30:52.729
[grunting, panting]

30:55.437 --> 30:57.729
[whimpering]

31:02.271 --> 31:03.354
[groans]

31:04.437 --> 31:05.437
Pull.

31:08.396 --> 31:09.854
Okay. You're okay.

31:09.937 --> 31:11.187
Tuk, Tuk. Hey.

31:15.521 --> 31:16.812
My sweet girl.

31:16.896 --> 31:18.021
Sweet girl.

31:18.104 --> 31:19.187
I'm so sorry.

31:19.271 --> 31:21.021
I'm so sorry.

31:24.521 --> 31:25.354
[people screaming in distance]

31:36.979 --> 31:37.812
What?

31:39.896 --> 31:41.729
Shit. Kiri, stay here.

31:43.229 --> 31:45.062
[breathing heavily]

31:46.312 --> 31:48.312
[screaming in distance]

31:49.771 --> 31:51.229
[exo-pack beeps]

32:00.271 --> 32:02.479
[gasps, shrieks]

32:15.354 --> 32:16.646
[grunts]

32:16.729 --> 32:19.521
[shouting]

32:28.146 --> 32:29.479
[chanting]

32:29.562 --> 32:31.229
Look. After them!

32:40.812 --> 32:41.646
Go, go.

32:43.354 --> 32:44.979
[ululating]

32:54.937 --> 32:56.146
[ululating, shrieking]

33:09.104 --> 33:10.854
[breathes shakily]

33:12.437 --> 33:13.812
[panting]

33:27.437 --> 33:28.437
One goes through.

33:29.479 --> 33:30.729
<c.s0>Tsahìk

33:37.271 --> 33:38.271
Knife.

33:45.437 --> 33:46.437
On me.

34:02.354 --> 34:04.062
[raider ululating]

34:08.979 --> 34:10.146
There!

34:10.229 --> 34:12.062
[raiders ululating]

34:17.729 --> 34:18.937
Kiri, come on.

34:19.021 --> 34:20.229
This way. Go, go.

34:22.312 --> 34:23.312
Keep going.

34:28.979 --> 34:29.896
Gotta get in the water. Come on.

34:30.437 --> 34:32.479
Go, go, go, go. Come on.

34:34.104 --> 34:35.771
Come on, swim!

34:39.729 --> 34:40.937
[Tuk] Lo'ak!

34:41.021 --> 34:42.854
I got you, Tuk. It's okay.

34:42.937 --> 34:44.062
What does Dad always say?

34:44.562 --> 34:46.104
Sullys stick together.

34:46.604 --> 34:47.604
No, the other one.

34:50.521 --> 34:51.562
Sullys never quit.

34:55.521 --> 34:56.521
[grunts] Nothing.

34:57.229 --> 34:58.062
Kiri.

34:59.562 --> 35:00.562
Hold on.

35:00.646 --> 35:01.896
[screams]

35:02.479 --> 35:03.354
[grunting]

35:04.312 --> 35:05.229
Kiri.

35:06.396 --> 35:07.229
Kiri.

35:08.812 --> 35:09.812
Spider.

35:12.854 --> 35:14.646
[grunting]

35:22.521 --> 35:23.646
Eagle Eye, do you copy?

35:40.604 --> 35:42.187
Neytiri, how copy?

35:45.229 --> 35:46.271
Neytiri, Neytiri,

35:46.354 --> 35:47.354
<c.s0>how copy?

35:49.271 --> 35:50.604
<c.s0>Neytiri, do you copy?

35:52.521 --> 35:53.521
What...

35:54.312 --> 35:55.312
Tuk.

35:57.104 --> 35:58.104
Swim.

35:59.021 --> 36:00.021
Go.

36:08.812 --> 36:10.104
[air hisses]

36:13.812 --> 36:15.062
Yeah, I'm good.

36:20.354 --> 36:22.271
[panting]

36:26.854 --> 36:29.479
No. Let's get out of sight.

36:29.562 --> 36:30.729
I wanna go home.

36:30.812 --> 36:32.021
[Lo'ak] Tuk, come on.

37:14.729 --> 37:16.312
[Jake breathing heavily]

37:27.312 --> 37:29.646
You stay real still now.

37:31.771 --> 37:32.854
[grunts]

37:33.562 --> 37:34.562
Is that all you got?

37:35.229 --> 37:37.354
All right. That'll do.

37:40.562 --> 37:41.771
Hands.

37:43.437 --> 37:45.312
I... I killed you.

37:55.729 --> 37:56.937
[groans]

38:00.479 --> 38:01.437
Help me.

38:04.937 --> 38:06.854
[coughing]

38:11.646 --> 38:13.729
[spits, sniffs]

38:13.812 --> 38:15.146
Who hit you, Corporal?

38:16.021 --> 38:17.312
<c.s0>Mangkwan

38:21.479 --> 38:22.854
[Quaritch] What's this?

38:22.937 --> 38:23.979
They cut the <c.s0>kuru

38:24.062 --> 38:26.021
They take their enemies' <c.s0>to'a

38:31.896 --> 38:32.979
Any sign of 'em?

38:33.062 --> 38:34.062
Kids are gone.

38:35.521 --> 38:36.521
That's fully charged,

38:38.521 --> 38:39.521
and he's running out.

38:39.604 --> 38:41.021
And that's if these Ash People

38:41.104 --> 38:42.896
don't get to him first.

38:49.854 --> 38:50.854
Can you track 'em?

38:52.937 --> 38:53.937
Can you track 'em?

38:54.437 --> 38:55.937
We're burning time, Colonel.

39:05.312 --> 39:06.604
[sighs]

39:08.771 --> 39:10.104
Again.

39:13.396 --> 39:14.729
Come on. This way.

39:28.229 --> 39:29.396
Spider.

39:29.479 --> 39:30.521
Bro.

39:35.771 --> 39:36.854
Look at me.

39:37.396 --> 39:38.604
Take slow breaths.

39:38.687 --> 39:39.937
Lo'ak...

39:41.437 --> 39:43.271
Come on, Bro. Horsey rides.

39:43.812 --> 39:44.812
Hop up.

39:46.979 --> 39:49.146
[groans, breathing heavily]

39:52.687 --> 39:53.687
[groans]

39:53.771 --> 39:55.437
[sobbing]

40:03.187 --> 40:04.521
The kids went in the water.

40:04.604 --> 40:05.771
Smart move.

40:15.437 --> 40:16.437
No, no, no.

40:24.354 --> 40:25.437
I beg you.

40:32.646 --> 40:33.646
Just breathe.

40:34.604 --> 40:35.604
Kiri.

40:49.229 --> 40:51.062
We're almost there.

40:51.146 --> 40:52.396
We can't sit around here.

40:52.479 --> 40:53.562
[normal] We have to go.

40:53.646 --> 40:55.021
Tuk, go get her.

40:55.562 --> 40:56.896
Kiri, come on.

40:56.979 --> 40:58.229
[groans]

40:58.312 --> 41:00.229
[breathing heavily]

41:02.604 --> 41:03.604
Stop.

41:05.187 --> 41:06.646
Bring him. Here.

41:06.729 --> 41:08.021
[Lo'ak] Kiri, stop.

41:10.604 --> 41:11.729
[echoing] Do as I say.

41:16.021 --> 41:17.312
[normal] Put him here.

41:22.271 --> 41:24.271
[breathing heavily]

41:25.562 --> 41:26.812
[Spider wheezes]

41:28.312 --> 41:29.562
[exo-pack beeping]

41:29.646 --> 41:30.896
[Spider choking]

41:30.979 --> 41:31.979
[Lo'ak] Stop.

41:32.062 --> 41:33.021
Kiri, what are you doing?

41:33.104 --> 41:34.104
What are you doing?

41:37.812 --> 41:39.146
What are you doing?

41:39.229 --> 41:40.312
I'm not sure.

41:41.187 --> 41:42.229
This feels right.

41:42.312 --> 41:43.312
What?

41:44.396 --> 41:45.979
Be quiet. I can't talk.

41:46.062 --> 41:46.937
[groans]

41:51.562 --> 41:54.354
[gasping weakly]

41:58.646 --> 41:59.812
Lo'ak. Lo'ak.

42:04.396 --> 42:07.062
[Kiri breathes rhythmically]

42:08.396 --> 42:09.729
[gasping weakly resumes]

42:16.271 --> 42:18.437
[beeping intensifies]

42:25.812 --> 42:28.104
[steady beep]

42:37.021 --> 42:38.687
Come on.

42:44.896 --> 42:46.687
[♪ dramatic music plays]

43:13.021 --> 43:15.187
[panting, moaning intensifies]

43:21.562 --> 43:22.396
Kiri.

43:22.479 --> 43:23.729
Kiri, Kiri.

43:27.187 --> 43:29.521
Lo'ak, no.

43:33.646 --> 43:36.312
[Kiri cries]

43:41.396 --> 43:42.854
Oh, no.

43:43.979 --> 43:45.354
I'm so sorry.

43:47.271 --> 43:48.271
I'm sorry.

43:59.646 --> 44:03.729
[crying]

44:03.812 --> 44:05.479
I'm so sorry.

44:09.521 --> 44:12.229
[gasps, coughing]

44:21.062 --> 44:22.354
Spider.

44:23.771 --> 44:25.854
[breathing heavily]

44:35.021 --> 44:36.396
[groans, spits]

44:40.187 --> 44:43.854
[breathing heavily]

44:43.937 --> 44:45.187
I'm breathing?

44:46.354 --> 44:47.312
Yes, Monkey Boy.

44:47.896 --> 44:49.229
You are.

44:50.312 --> 44:51.687
[Kiri chuckles]

44:52.771 --> 44:54.021
I'm dead.

44:54.937 --> 44:56.646
This is the Spirit World.

45:00.437 --> 45:02.312
[breathes deeply]

45:02.396 --> 45:03.854
I'm breathing the air.

45:04.729 --> 45:05.729
Yeah.

45:06.479 --> 45:07.729
I'm breathing the air!

45:08.979 --> 45:10.146
I'm breathing the air!

45:10.812 --> 45:11.896
I'm breathing the air!

45:15.937 --> 45:17.062
Whoo!

45:17.146 --> 45:18.354
Yeah, I'm breathing the air,

45:18.437 --> 45:19.437
baby!

45:20.229 --> 45:22.187
Bro, Bro, quiet. Quiet.

45:25.854 --> 45:26.854
Thank you.

45:27.812 --> 45:28.812
[Kiri] Spider.

45:28.896 --> 45:30.896
Whatever you did. Thank you.

45:33.229 --> 45:34.604
Shit. Get back.

45:34.687 --> 45:35.687
Kiri.

45:39.812 --> 45:41.562
[raiders ululating, shouting]

45:43.729 --> 45:44.854
We're cut off.

45:46.312 --> 45:47.312
[Spider] Bro!

45:47.396 --> 45:48.396
[Tuk] Behind us.

45:53.062 --> 45:54.687
[Tuk screams]

45:56.312 --> 45:58.271
[hisses, grunts]

45:58.354 --> 45:59.521
No!

45:59.604 --> 46:00.604
Kiri!

46:07.062 --> 46:08.187
[raider] <c.s0>Tsahìk.

46:14.354 --> 46:15.771
Ah.

46:30.104 --> 46:31.729
[Kiri sobbing]

46:38.437 --> 46:39.646
We gotta get in there.

46:41.604 --> 46:44.062
Is not our air

46:44.146 --> 46:45.354
poison

46:46.062 --> 46:47.521
to Sky People?

46:51.937 --> 46:52.937
[snarls]

46:54.187 --> 46:55.604
How

46:56.479 --> 46:58.479
do you still live,

46:58.562 --> 46:59.729
air breather?

46:59.812 --> 47:00.937
[snarls]

47:04.104 --> 47:05.354
[raiders snarl]

47:09.896 --> 47:11.396
Eywa?

47:12.229 --> 47:13.479
Yes.

47:16.271 --> 47:18.521
If I cut now,

47:25.271 --> 47:26.479
Do you think?

47:27.021 --> 47:28.021
[raiders laugh, snarl]

47:29.479 --> 47:30.646
No.

47:31.396 --> 47:33.271
Your goddess

47:33.354 --> 47:36.187
has no dominion here.

47:36.729 --> 47:37.729
Come on.

47:38.437 --> 47:39.521
Now give me the knife.

47:44.354 --> 47:45.354
Colonel.

47:53.687 --> 47:54.687
You...

48:09.104 --> 48:09.937
I can't.

48:12.021 --> 48:13.312
[Varang] Make thunder.

48:15.521 --> 48:16.646
Make it work.

48:20.146 --> 48:21.312
there's no thunder.

48:21.812 --> 48:23.146
Kill the youngest one.

48:26.562 --> 48:29.562
[shouts, grunting]

48:30.437 --> 48:32.896
[raiders grunting, ululating]

48:39.479 --> 48:41.187
Weapons down!

48:44.062 --> 48:45.271
[screams]

48:45.354 --> 48:46.354
Down!

48:46.437 --> 48:47.562
<c.s0>Mangkwan

48:48.396 --> 48:50.562
Now get back. Back.

48:52.479 --> 48:53.479
[snarls]

48:55.854 --> 48:56.812
Stay back.

49:02.021 --> 49:03.229
Sully, we good?

49:05.312 --> 49:06.729
All right.

49:08.604 --> 49:09.646
[sobbing]

49:12.479 --> 49:13.354
Keep moving.

49:23.812 --> 49:25.812
[shouts]

49:25.896 --> 49:26.854
No!

49:26.937 --> 49:27.771
Dad!

49:30.229 --> 49:31.146
[Tuk] Dad!

49:33.896 --> 49:34.896
[Wainfleet] Come on.

49:34.979 --> 49:35.979
Move.

49:48.854 --> 49:50.854
[breathing heavily]

49:57.437 --> 49:59.146
[raiders laughing]

50:02.229 --> 50:03.646
[snarls]

50:04.937 --> 50:06.646
You are strong,

50:07.354 --> 50:09.021
Sky Man.

50:09.729 --> 50:10.729
[Tuk whimpers]

50:14.062 --> 50:15.229
You...

50:28.479 --> 50:29.479
See?

50:32.354 --> 50:34.312
And now you take aim.

50:34.396 --> 50:35.937
What do you want to hit?

50:37.771 --> 50:39.437
Well, just go like this.

50:42.479 --> 50:43.479
[raiders gasp]

50:43.562 --> 50:44.646
Yeah.

50:47.354 --> 50:48.437
Go on.

50:49.146 --> 50:50.146
[grunts]

50:59.104 --> 51:00.229
Uh-huh.

51:02.396 --> 51:04.521
[Varang, raiders ululating]

51:15.396 --> 51:17.312
[raiders chuckling]

51:26.437 --> 51:28.271
You, you. Come with me.

51:30.562 --> 51:31.562
Clear the way!

51:32.479 --> 51:33.479
Neytiri!

51:33.562 --> 51:34.521
[Neytiri breathes shakily]

51:34.604 --> 51:37.521
Cut her down. Cut her down. Hold her.

51:38.979 --> 51:40.062
[shushes] Neytiri, we got you.

51:42.396 --> 51:43.396
[Norm] We got you.

51:43.896 --> 51:45.937
Max, prep for surgery. Go.

51:46.021 --> 51:47.229
Open both doors.

51:47.979 --> 51:49.979
[cheering, chanting]

51:51.271 --> 51:53.312
[chanting in Na'vi]

51:58.646 --> 51:59.979
[grunting]

52:01.187 --> 52:02.812
[straining]

52:04.437 --> 52:05.854
[Jake groans]

52:09.646 --> 52:11.729
[chanting in Na'vi]

52:11.812 --> 52:13.104
[grunts]

52:24.187 --> 52:26.604
[♪ mysterious music plays]

52:54.021 --> 52:57.271
[breathing heavily]

53:16.312 --> 53:17.604
[hisses]

53:19.729 --> 53:21.437
[grunting, choking]

53:23.604 --> 53:24.979
[whooping, ululating]

53:25.604 --> 53:27.562
[choking, gagging]

53:28.104 --> 53:29.229
[grunts]

53:40.146 --> 53:41.687
[chanting continues]

53:45.896 --> 53:47.479
[panting, grunting]

53:49.604 --> 53:50.604
Guys, come on.

53:51.104 --> 53:51.937
[grunts]

53:56.979 --> 53:59.062
[whooping]

54:04.479 --> 54:05.979
[clamoring]

54:08.812 --> 54:09.812
It was the girl.

54:10.562 --> 54:11.729
Come on. Get in.

54:12.312 --> 54:13.146
This way.

54:13.229 --> 54:14.229
Let's go.

54:16.104 --> 54:16.937
Come on.

54:30.187 --> 54:31.312
<c.s0>Tsahìk.

54:33.604 --> 54:34.771
They are gone.

54:37.604 --> 54:39.187
We search by air.

54:39.271 --> 54:41.479
[speaking Na'vi]

54:48.229 --> 54:49.229
Tarsem.

54:50.437 --> 54:51.812
What? Oh.

54:51.896 --> 54:53.271
Easy, easy. Max!

54:55.187 --> 54:56.937
No. Stop it. Stop her.

55:00.104 --> 55:01.479
Daughter, calm.

55:04.021 --> 55:05.271
Where?

55:05.354 --> 55:06.729
[breathing shakily]

55:06.812 --> 55:08.062
Where are they?

55:08.146 --> 55:09.854
[insects chirping]

55:11.354 --> 55:12.396
[Tuk grunts]

55:27.812 --> 55:28.812
We're hot.

55:28.896 --> 55:30.146
All right. Don't even calibrate.

55:30.979 --> 55:31.812
[grunts]

55:31.896 --> 55:34.187
No. You must rest, my child.

55:38.854 --> 55:40.104
[straining] I will ride.

55:41.854 --> 55:43.604
[insects chirping]

55:50.562 --> 55:53.312
[pants, grunts]

55:53.396 --> 55:54.396
I've got you.

56:00.354 --> 56:01.729
[breathing shakily]

56:02.521 --> 56:03.521
[Spider] This is good.

56:03.604 --> 56:04.896
[Tuk mumbles]

56:07.187 --> 56:08.229
[Kiri] Lie down.

56:10.854 --> 56:13.021
[grunts, sighs]

56:14.521 --> 56:15.562
We're clear.

56:15.646 --> 56:16.646
Yeah.

56:17.687 --> 56:19.479
Which brings us to our...

56:20.229 --> 56:21.729
unresolved issues.

56:26.729 --> 56:28.104
Well, I'm out of arrows.

56:30.854 --> 56:32.729
Still got our knives.

56:38.312 --> 56:39.521
Yeah, well I'm kind of tired.

56:40.729 --> 56:43.437
[chuckles] Yeah.

56:44.604 --> 56:45.896
Yeah, better save it.

56:48.062 --> 56:49.062
In case those...

56:51.729 --> 56:54.979
[breathing heavily, sighs]

56:55.062 --> 56:56.104
Yeah, sure.

57:05.437 --> 57:07.187
[insects chirping]

57:11.229 --> 57:12.521
He's a good kid.

57:12.604 --> 57:14.062
[♪ hopeful music plays]

57:18.146 --> 57:19.854
Hey, uh, this don't mean

57:23.187 --> 57:24.729
I'm still bringing you in.

57:24.812 --> 57:27.062
Dead, if I have to.

57:34.229 --> 57:36.771
This world goes much deeper

57:36.854 --> 57:38.187
than you imagine.

57:40.062 --> 57:42.354
You witnessed it tonight.

57:43.771 --> 57:44.771
With her.

57:46.187 --> 57:47.687
And with him.

57:48.729 --> 57:49.937
Don't matter.

58:11.521 --> 58:13.896
[sighs]

58:27.271 --> 58:28.687
[ikran shrieks]

58:28.771 --> 58:29.896
It's them.

58:29.979 --> 58:30.896
It's the Ash.

58:34.354 --> 58:35.521
Come on. We got to move.

58:36.604 --> 58:38.396
[ululating]

58:38.937 --> 58:39.979
It's okay. It's okay.

58:41.562 --> 58:42.521
[whooping]

58:42.604 --> 58:43.604
Tarsem! [whoops]

58:50.187 --> 58:53.062
Kiri, Tuk, are you hurt?

58:53.146 --> 58:54.354
[Kiri] How did you find us?

58:55.854 --> 58:57.437
[Neytiri] Children!

59:00.812 --> 59:02.771
Tuk. Tuk. Kiri.

59:03.396 --> 59:04.604
Lo'ak.

59:09.187 --> 59:10.396
Are you okay? [sobs]

59:10.479 --> 59:11.687
Come here. It's okay.

59:11.771 --> 59:12.729
We're okay.

59:14.854 --> 59:16.146
[Spider] Hey, Norm.

59:16.229 --> 59:17.562
[♪ hopeful music plays]

59:18.479 --> 59:19.479
What's up?

59:22.729 --> 59:23.729
What?

59:25.354 --> 59:26.354
What...

59:26.437 --> 59:27.521
Dude.

59:28.562 --> 59:29.396
Oh.

59:32.021 --> 59:34.312
[♪ majestic music plays]

59:38.646 --> 59:39.729
[shrieks]

59:40.396 --> 59:42.312
[gasps] Tuktirey.

59:42.812 --> 59:44.146
[chuckles] Kiri.

59:51.771 --> 59:52.771
We're inbound

59:52.854 --> 59:54.104
at the city wall.

59:54.979 --> 59:55.979
[music ends]

59:56.062 --> 59:57.979
[machines beeping]

01:00:08.104 --> 01:00:09.396
I'd make book on it.

01:00:09.479 --> 01:00:11.437
This is not my priority.

01:00:15.729 --> 01:00:16.729
And who do you think

01:00:32.062 --> 01:00:33.021
Not many more.

01:00:34.229 --> 01:00:35.104
Don't be a baby.

01:00:36.437 --> 01:00:37.521
Now, you see this?

01:00:37.604 --> 01:00:39.104
This is all mycelium.

01:00:40.646 --> 01:00:41.646
as the forest network.

01:00:41.729 --> 01:00:42.729
Somehow,

01:00:42.812 --> 01:00:43.896
it colonized him,

01:00:53.062 --> 01:00:54.271
Can you get it out?

01:00:55.354 --> 01:00:56.937
No, it's an endosymbiont.

01:01:03.896 --> 01:01:04.729
he's alive.

01:01:08.396 --> 01:01:09.396
A good thing?

01:01:11.437 --> 01:01:12.687
