01:28:31.979 --> 01:28:33.104
you need me.

01:28:38.937 --> 01:28:40.187
I See you.

01:28:42.229 --> 01:28:43.771
Damn right you do.

01:29:26.146 --> 01:29:28.062
[laughs]

01:29:42.271 --> 01:29:44.437
[whooping, clamoring]

01:29:51.271 --> 01:29:53.271
[♪ majestic music plays]

01:30:00.979 --> 01:30:03.354
[sighs]

01:30:03.437 --> 01:30:05.562
When I can connect again,

01:30:05.646 --> 01:30:06.812
someday,

01:30:07.854 --> 01:30:09.146
whenever,

01:30:13.562 --> 01:30:16.229
Well, can I just go now?

01:30:16.312 --> 01:30:17.187
No.

01:30:28.771 --> 01:30:32.187
[bellows]

01:30:34.521 --> 01:30:36.854
They're starting to arrive

01:30:36.937 --> 01:30:38.562
for the Calf Communion.

01:30:38.646 --> 01:30:40.437
[bellows]

01:30:40.521 --> 01:30:41.771
Yearling calves

01:30:41.854 --> 01:30:44.312
and reef babies together

01:30:46.937 --> 01:30:48.187
It'll be so beautiful.

01:30:51.479 --> 01:30:52.729
[bellows]

01:30:58.646 --> 01:31:03.604
[grunting, sighing]

01:31:16.021 --> 01:31:17.021
Let me see.

01:31:19.562 --> 01:31:21.146
Looks good.

01:31:21.229 --> 01:31:22.771
I like this on you.

01:31:22.854 --> 01:31:23.854
Come to the festival.

01:31:24.396 --> 01:31:25.479
No, no, no, no.

01:31:40.771 --> 01:31:42.104
my <c.s0>tulkun

01:31:46.896 --> 01:31:47.896
Where?

01:31:49.312 --> 01:31:52.062
<c.s0>Tulkun

01:31:52.562 --> 01:31:53.604
