01:32:11.562 --> 01:32:15.104
[inhales sharply, whimpers]

01:32:17.604 --> 01:32:19.437
[sobs]

01:32:20.604 --> 01:32:21.729
[sighs]

01:32:23.312 --> 01:32:24.687
Lo'ak.

01:32:28.812 --> 01:32:29.812
Bye, Mom.

01:32:31.187 --> 01:32:32.271
Where are you going?

01:32:34.604 --> 01:32:35.604
Just out.

01:32:45.312 --> 01:32:46.687
[breathes shakily]

01:32:47.646 --> 01:32:48.646
[Tsireya] Lo'ak!

01:32:51.062 --> 01:32:52.062
Lo'ak!

01:32:54.229 --> 01:32:55.354
Lo'ak, wait!

01:32:57.229 --> 01:32:58.229
Lo'ak.

01:33:00.354 --> 01:33:01.562
[sighs]

01:33:14.854 --> 01:33:16.021
We cannot go.

01:33:20.521 --> 01:33:21.604
We are going.

01:33:22.937 --> 01:33:23.979
All of us.

01:33:26.812 --> 01:33:27.812
Tell no one.

01:33:30.396 --> 01:33:32.729
