01:33:38.104 --> 01:33:39.104
You let them?

01:33:39.687 --> 01:33:41.021
They did not ask.

01:33:42.771 --> 01:33:43.896
We'll go after them.

01:33:47.771 --> 01:33:49.187
if the demon ships come.

01:33:56.687 --> 01:33:58.396
This is his path.

01:34:03.187 --> 01:34:04.604
Look at what he did.

01:34:08.437 --> 01:34:10.271
