01:34:11.437 --> 01:34:12.771
You must trust that.

01:34:19.062 --> 01:34:20.187
The way of water

01:34:20.271 --> 01:34:21.312
has no beginning...

01:34:24.729 --> 01:34:25.729
and no end.

01:34:25.812 --> 01:34:26.812
The sea is your home...

01:34:32.396 --> 01:34:33.437
before your birth...

01:34:40.437 --> 01:34:41.812
and after your death.

01:34:52.146 --> 01:34:53.354
[gasping]

01:34:56.479 --> 01:34:57.562
[screams]

01:34:57.646 --> 01:34:59.729
[groans, breathing heavily]

01:35:01.062 --> 01:35:02.062
[gasps]

01:35:04.104 --> 01:35:05.979
Where is the one

01:35:06.062 --> 01:35:07.854
Toruk Makto

01:35:10.229 --> 01:35:11.062
One, two.

01:35:11.146 --> 01:35:12.979
How many birds are in the sky?

01:35:13.062 --> 01:35:14.521
One, two, three--

01:35:14.604 --> 01:35:15.812
[both laugh]

01:35:20.187 --> 01:35:21.229
No.

01:35:23.937 --> 01:35:24.937
[chuckles] <c.s0>Skxawng

01:35:25.021 --> 01:35:26.437
Just a little bit.

01:35:26.521 --> 01:35:27.687
A couple of centimeters.

01:35:29.646 --> 01:35:30.896
She's the All Mother.

01:35:30.979 --> 01:35:32.062
She can do anything.

01:35:34.562 --> 01:35:35.729
You are perfect

01:35:35.812 --> 01:35:37.396
just the way you are.

01:35:57.396 --> 01:35:58.646
Come on, Monkey Boy.

01:36:00.187 --> 01:36:01.187
[chuckles]

01:36:02.021 --> 01:36:03.021
So next thing is,

01:36:07.604 --> 01:36:08.812
and protect us all.

01:36:13.312 --> 01:36:14.146
What is it?

01:36:15.521 --> 01:36:16.437
[Kiri gasps]

01:36:16.521 --> 01:36:18.021
Sh-- [grunts]

01:36:19.479 --> 01:36:20.521
[warriors whooping, shouting]

01:36:21.354 --> 01:36:22.187
