01:36:22.687 --> 01:36:23.562
Run!

01:36:25.187 --> 01:36:26.729
[Mangkwan grunting, whooping]

01:36:30.271 --> 01:36:31.437
[breathing heavily] Hurry!

01:36:32.812 --> 01:36:33.854
