01:36:35.646 --> 01:36:36.479
[panting] Spider.

01:36:37.062 --> 01:36:38.354
Over here, assholes!

01:36:38.437 --> 01:36:39.604
[whooping]

01:36:40.521 --> 01:36:41.646
[Spider] Come on!

01:36:41.729 --> 01:36:42.812
Hey, <c.s0>skxawng

01:36:43.646 --> 01:36:44.812
This way, you bastards!

01:36:46.812 --> 01:36:48.062
Come on, dipshits!

01:36:48.979 --> 01:36:50.312
Is that all you got?

01:36:50.396 --> 01:36:51.937
[whooping continues]

01:36:52.021 --> 01:36:53.021
Shit!

01:36:55.896 --> 01:36:57.521
Settle down there, cowboy.

01:37:02.604 --> 01:37:04.312
Air breather.

01:37:09.187 --> 01:37:12.021
[screaming]

01:37:12.104 --> 01:37:12.937
[snarls]

01:37:13.021 --> 01:37:15.604
[groans, grunts]

01:37:16.271 --> 01:37:17.271
[grunts]

01:37:18.104 --> 01:37:18.979
[snarls]

01:37:19.062 --> 01:37:20.271
We fly.

01:37:26.562 --> 01:37:29.229
[nightwraiths shrieking]

01:37:35.854 --> 01:37:37.521
[breathing heavily]

01:37:41.687 --> 01:37:43.687
[♪ dramatic music playing]

01:37:50.396 --> 01:37:51.312
Weapons!

01:37:51.396 --> 01:37:52.562
Where's your sister?

01:37:52.646 --> 01:37:53.687
She went for water.

01:38:00.687 --> 01:38:02.604
