01:38:15.604 --> 01:38:16.604
Take him.

01:38:20.187 --> 01:38:21.312
[roars]

01:38:23.979 --> 01:38:24.979
[shrieks]

01:38:37.437 --> 01:38:38.604
Be calm.

01:38:39.146 --> 01:38:40.521
No fear.

01:38:41.271 --> 01:38:42.271
No fear!

01:38:49.854 --> 01:38:51.146
Jake Sully!

01:38:54.354 --> 01:38:55.479
I will not go without you.

01:38:56.104 --> 01:38:57.937
No. They got Spider.

01:39:00.979 --> 01:39:02.354
These people will die.

01:39:02.437 --> 01:39:04.312
You cannot ask this.

01:39:04.396 --> 01:39:05.979
Husband, I cannot.

01:39:07.604 --> 01:39:09.396
This is the only way.

01:39:10.187 --> 01:39:11.479
[Quaritch] Jake Sully!

01:39:11.562 --> 01:39:13.479
Show yourself!

01:39:15.604 --> 01:39:17.687
Take your sister. Go and hide.

01:39:18.604 --> 01:39:19.604
Go!

01:39:19.687 --> 01:39:20.979
