01:39:21.062 --> 01:39:22.396
If you stay, I stay.

01:39:22.479 --> 01:39:24.146
I will kill many!

01:39:27.146 --> 01:39:28.562
You swear to me.

01:39:29.521 --> 01:39:30.937
