01:39:31.604 --> 01:39:33.187
I know he's here.

01:39:33.271 --> 01:39:34.479
Give him to me.

01:39:36.312 --> 01:39:37.479
He is one of us.

01:39:38.104 --> 01:39:39.521
He is one of us!

01:39:40.437 --> 01:39:42.062
Burn something.

01:39:45.979 --> 01:39:47.229
Switching incendiaries.

01:39:53.396 --> 01:39:55.937
[Metkayina screaming, clamoring]

01:40:01.271 --> 01:40:03.271
[Mangkwan cheering, ululating]

01:40:03.354 --> 01:40:05.312
I want Jake Sully!

01:40:08.812 --> 01:40:10.604
Hold your fire. Stop.

01:40:11.396 --> 01:40:12.396
Hold fire.

01:40:18.937 --> 01:40:20.187
[sighs]

01:40:21.146 --> 01:40:22.146
[hisses]

01:40:27.146 --> 01:40:27.979
[hisses]

01:40:28.062 --> 01:40:29.521
[snarls]

01:40:37.062 --> 01:40:38.312
Colonel.

01:40:39.021 --> 01:40:40.021
Corporal.

01:40:40.646 --> 01:40:42.104
You take me,

01:40:52.437 --> 01:40:53.729
[Jake] You get me.

01:40:58.312 --> 01:41:00.687
Pregnant ladies, kids.

01:41:03.687 --> 01:41:05.021
