01:41:31.896 --> 01:41:33.646
When I drop my arm,

01:41:40.562 --> 01:41:41.771
Maybe.

01:41:45.271 --> 01:41:46.479
Maybe we bum rush ya,

01:41:54.604 --> 01:41:55.896
