01:42:08.937 --> 01:42:10.021
Safety

01:42:10.979 --> 01:42:12.396
for these people.

01:42:12.979 --> 01:42:14.812
Burn them all, Quaritch.

01:42:14.896 --> 01:42:16.562
[♪ tense music plays]

01:42:16.646 --> 01:42:18.021
[snarls]

01:42:24.396 --> 01:42:25.812
