01:42:30.687 --> 01:42:31.687
Done.

01:42:33.104 --> 01:42:34.771
Want to pinky swear?

01:42:39.979 --> 01:42:41.896
[breathing heavily]

01:42:44.021 --> 01:42:45.021
[Quaritch] Take him.

01:42:46.729 --> 01:42:47.729
Turn around.

01:42:50.021 --> 01:42:51.979
[Neytiri breathing heavily]

01:42:53.771 --> 01:42:54.771
Move.

01:43:01.229 --> 01:43:02.354
[yells]

01:43:07.396 --> 01:43:09.812
[breathing heavily]

01:43:15.937 --> 01:43:17.062
Another time then,

01:43:17.146 --> 01:43:18.146
Mrs. Sully.

01:43:18.229 --> 01:43:19.354
[snarls]

01:43:22.521 --> 01:43:23.521
Saddle up.

01:43:29.729 --> 01:43:31.687
[breathing shakily]

01:44:00.479 --> 01:44:03.437
[beeping]

01:44:06.854 --> 01:44:07.854
What do we got?

01:44:12.812 --> 01:44:14.271
Weapons locked out.

01:44:16.604 --> 01:44:17.562
Expand it.

01:44:30.021 --> 01:44:31.187
[shrieks]

01:44:33.021 --> 01:44:34.271
[roars]

01:44:34.354 --> 01:44:35.979
[crowd clamoring]

01:44:39.604 --> 01:44:41.937
[breathing heavily]

01:44:58.229 --> 01:45:00.187
[in Na'vi]

01:45:11.062 --> 01:45:12.562
Easy, easy.

01:45:12.646 --> 01:45:13.687
Let's go.

01:45:16.604 --> 01:45:18.021
[soldier 2] Let's go. Move.

01:45:24.062 --> 01:45:25.062
Jake!

01:45:25.729 --> 01:45:26.729
[soldier 3] Up.

01:45:33.146 --> 01:45:34.146
[grunts]

01:45:44.604 --> 01:45:45.854
Jake Sully.

01:45:45.937 --> 01:45:47.771
<c.s0>Toruk Makto

01:45:48.354 --> 01:45:49.812
[clamoring]

01:45:50.312 --> 01:45:52.646
[breathing deeply]

01:46:08.437 --> 01:46:09.271
[speaks Na'vi]

01:46:09.354 --> 01:46:10.354
[speaks Na'vi]

01:46:10.437 --> 01:46:11.771
[in English] Not hostiles.

01:46:11.854 --> 01:46:13.104
Allies.

01:46:16.521 --> 01:46:18.312
<c.s0>Tsahìk Mangkwan

01:46:26.146 --> 01:46:27.854
escorted off my base

01:46:27.937 --> 01:46:28.979
ASAP,

01:46:33.062 --> 01:46:34.687
[sighs]

01:46:35.521 --> 01:46:37.229
[inhales deeply]

01:46:41.312 --> 01:46:42.437
Take the win.

01:46:47.104 --> 01:46:48.896
Huh? [chuckles]

01:46:49.937 --> 01:46:51.396
End of an era!

01:47:06.896 --> 01:47:08.062
Yeah!

01:47:08.146 --> 01:47:09.062
Whoo!

01:47:09.562 --> 01:47:10.479
<c.s0>Tsahìk.

01:47:10.562 --> 01:47:11.687
[chuckles]

01:47:11.771 --> 01:47:12.604
[chuckles]

01:47:13.146 --> 01:47:14.146
Let's go.

01:47:15.062 --> 01:47:17.062
[♪ dramatic music plays]

01:47:30.062 --> 01:47:31.396
[struggling, snarling]

01:47:31.479 --> 01:47:32.646
[nurse] Easy, easy.

01:47:43.521 --> 01:47:44.354
[screams]

01:47:46.062 --> 01:47:47.062
Almost there.

01:47:52.812 --> 01:47:53.812
[growls]

01:47:55.812 --> 01:47:56.812
Payakan!

01:47:57.854 --> 01:47:59.062
[squeaks]

01:48:00.354 --> 01:48:01.354
Payakan!

01:48:08.396 --> 01:48:09.312
The People say

01:48:09.396 --> 01:48:11.354
<c.s0>the sea washes you clean.

01:48:11.437 --> 01:48:12.479
Payakan!

01:48:15.729 --> 01:48:16.729
It's Lo'ak.

01:48:18.896 --> 01:48:20.062
[Aonung] <c.s0>Skxawng

01:48:20.146 --> 01:48:21.146
Lo'ak!

01:48:21.229 --> 01:48:22.187
Tsireya!

01:48:22.271 --> 01:48:24.146
[honking]

01:48:26.479 --> 01:48:29.062
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>They also say,
if you see the deep ones,

01:48:29.146 --> 01:48:30.312
<c.s0>the

01:48:33.396 --> 01:48:35.229
<c.s0>they're spirits
sent to judge you.

01:48:43.812 --> 01:48:44.646
[squeaks]

01:48:48.104 --> 01:48:49.437
-<c.s0>Tsyong

01:48:55.646 --> 01:48:56.479
[gasps]

01:49:00.562 --> 01:49:01.396
[grunts]

01:49:13.312 --> 01:49:14.146
[grunts]

01:49:27.771 --> 01:49:29.104
[grunting]

01:49:31.021 --> 01:49:32.104
[straining]

01:49:41.937 --> 01:49:42.979
[grunts]

01:49:50.354 --> 01:49:51.937
[bellows]

01:49:53.437 --> 01:49:55.396
