01:50:04.812 --> 01:50:06.729
[echoing] Lo'ak. Lo'ak.

01:50:06.812 --> 01:50:08.562
Lo'ak! Lo'ak!

01:50:09.312 --> 01:50:11.021
[coughing]

01:50:13.062 --> 01:50:14.062
Tsireya.

01:50:17.604 --> 01:50:18.604
[sighs]

01:50:18.687 --> 01:50:19.896
[chuckles]

01:50:23.479 --> 01:50:24.479
Let him go.

01:50:24.562 --> 01:50:25.937
[breathing heavily]

01:50:30.271 --> 01:50:31.604
[chuckles]

01:50:37.229 --> 01:50:38.229
Is this your Sister?

01:50:38.312 --> 01:50:39.312
Yes.

01:50:57.937 --> 01:50:59.729
Yes, it's an endosymbiont.

01:51:06.896 --> 01:51:08.146
[grunts]

01:51:08.229 --> 01:51:11.396
[grunting]

01:51:14.854 --> 01:51:15.854
[gasps]

01:51:20.812 --> 01:51:21.812
Where's Jake?

01:51:24.937 --> 01:51:25.937
Here.

01:51:27.062 --> 01:51:29.021
I brought you a burger.

01:51:29.104 --> 01:51:30.187
You better not hurt him.

01:51:33.104 --> 01:51:34.354
You're with me now.

01:51:34.437 --> 01:51:35.771
[chuckles]

01:51:35.854 --> 01:51:36.854
I'm your father.

01:51:37.396 --> 01:51:38.562
My father's dead.

01:51:43.437 --> 01:51:45.062
No, no. No.

01:51:48.021 --> 01:51:49.062
Yeah, look.

01:51:51.396 --> 01:51:52.521
[scoffs]

01:51:52.604 --> 01:51:53.604
Deceased.

01:51:56.604 --> 01:51:58.354
[inhales deeply, sighs]

01:51:59.562 --> 01:52:00.562
to talk too much

01:52:04.354 --> 01:52:05.521
I gotta thank you.

01:52:09.854 --> 01:52:11.021
You saved my life.

01:52:15.771 --> 01:52:16.937
Maybe that's true.

01:52:20.271 --> 01:52:21.354
Either way,

01:52:22.271 --> 01:52:23.437
I owe you.

01:52:27.937 --> 01:52:29.646
Man, I'm proud of you.

01:52:34.812 --> 01:52:37.104
guts, smarts, and...

01:52:49.437 --> 01:52:50.437
and that's your mother.

01:52:50.521 --> 01:52:51.604
[chuckles]

01:52:51.687 --> 01:52:52.687
Oh, man.

01:52:52.771 --> 01:52:55.271
She was, uh, ferocious.

01:52:56.896 --> 01:52:58.437
Tough to live with, but...

01:53:00.187 --> 01:53:01.396
I loved her.

01:53:10.187 --> 01:53:11.521
going into battle,

01:53:14.312 --> 01:53:15.437
[sighs]

01:53:20.771 --> 01:53:21.771
You got that

01:53:21.854 --> 01:53:22.854
in you too.

01:53:25.187 --> 01:53:26.062
Anyway,

01:53:26.146 --> 01:53:27.229
I didn't come down here

01:53:32.354 --> 01:53:34.687
If you need me.

01:53:37.146 --> 01:53:38.312
I'm here for you.

01:53:42.187 --> 01:53:43.229
Can I keep it?

01:53:54.104 --> 01:53:55.354
Eat something, will you?

01:54:06.771 --> 01:54:07.771
[Lo'ak] Brother!

01:54:12.646 --> 01:54:14.146
[singing]

01:54:15.021 --> 01:54:16.604
I See you, Brother.

01:54:22.896 --> 01:54:23.812
What is it?

01:54:23.896 --> 01:54:24.812
What's wrong?

01:54:25.646 --> 01:54:26.812
[rumbling]

01:54:32.396 --> 01:54:33.896
[singing]

01:54:45.687 --> 01:54:47.729
[singing]

01:55:00.021 --> 01:55:01.771
<c.s0>Tulkun

01:55:22.604 --> 01:55:23.604
Who are you?

01:55:28.729 --> 01:55:29.729
These creatures,

01:55:32.937 --> 01:55:33.937
This is organized.

01:55:39.562 --> 01:55:40.562
We all made our deals.

01:55:42.729 --> 01:55:43.812
[Ardmore] Dr. Garvin.

01:55:43.896 --> 01:55:45.021
Dr. Garvin, thank you.

01:55:57.146 --> 01:55:58.437
against the islands.

01:56:09.104 --> 01:56:10.396
