02:47:13.021 --> 02:47:14.021
[Quaritch] Mrs. Sully.

02:47:17.021 --> 02:47:18.229
[shouts]

02:47:19.979 --> 02:47:21.187
[breathing heavily]

02:47:21.729 --> 02:47:22.729
[shouts]

02:47:27.021 --> 02:47:28.812
[shouts, panting]

02:47:34.021 --> 02:47:34.937
Spoils of war.

02:47:44.312 --> 02:47:46.146
[roars]

02:47:46.229 --> 02:47:47.229
[grunts]

02:47:48.146 --> 02:47:49.979
[panting]

02:47:50.479 --> 02:47:51.646
I need you now.

02:47:53.312 --> 02:47:54.521
By my side.

02:47:54.604 --> 02:47:56.687
I need my wingman.

02:48:03.021 --> 02:48:04.021
[grunts]

02:48:15.062 --> 02:48:16.146
<c.s0>I know you can hear me.

02:48:20.646 --> 02:48:21.646
[shrieks, groaning]

02:48:26.021 --> 02:48:26.854
No!

02:48:37.687 --> 02:48:39.854
[pants]

02:48:39.937 --> 02:48:42.812
