02:49:30.396 --> 02:49:32.396
Matadors, ahead slow.

02:49:32.479 --> 02:49:33.687
Even spacing.

02:49:35.104 --> 02:49:36.104
Sub teams,

02:49:36.187 --> 02:49:38.021
