02:49:38.104 --> 02:49:39.437
Arm torpedoes.

02:49:41.437 --> 02:49:42.521
Sixty meters.

02:49:49.312 --> 02:49:50.479
[tulkun rumbling, squealing]

02:49:51.271 --> 02:49:52.437
Safeties off.

02:49:56.104 --> 02:49:57.437
Stand by to fire.

02:49:58.604 --> 02:50:00.479
[♪ dramatic music plays]

02:50:08.687 --> 02:50:10.062
Look.

02:50:24.687 --> 02:50:25.687
Hold your fire.

02:50:26.229 --> 02:50:27.437
Hold fire for what?

02:50:30.021 --> 02:50:31.271
It's Eywa. It worked.

02:50:32.312 --> 02:50:33.312
It worked.

02:50:51.771 --> 02:50:54.437
[♪ dramatic music continues]

02:50:54.521 --> 02:50:55.437
Look out!

02:50:56.354 --> 02:50:57.187
[gunner 3] Get us out of here.

02:50:58.604 --> 02:50:59.521
[shouting]

02:51:07.021 --> 02:51:08.312
[screams]

02:51:08.396 --> 02:51:09.396
[crew member 1] Whoa.

02:51:09.479 --> 02:51:10.896
[crew member 2] Look out!

02:51:10.979 --> 02:51:12.729
[screaming, clamoring]

02:51:23.062 --> 02:51:24.062
to the ship.

02:51:26.271 --> 02:51:27.354
Yeah.

02:51:27.437 --> 02:51:29.062
That's right, buttholes.

02:51:35.437 --> 02:51:37.312
[roars]

02:51:41.396 --> 02:51:42.479
[ikran shrieks]

02:51:43.354 --> 02:51:45.562
[shouting]

02:51:51.771 --> 02:51:53.646
[whooping, ululating]

02:52:02.646 --> 02:52:03.646
[screaming]

02:52:05.979 --> 02:52:07.354
Oh, God.

02:52:19.979 --> 02:52:21.479
[roars]

02:52:49.729 --> 02:52:50.937
[sighs]

02:52:56.229 --> 02:52:58.312
[rumbles, bellows]

02:52:58.396 --> 02:52:59.771
[breathing heavily]

02:53:05.687 --> 02:53:08.104
[exclaiming, screaming]

02:53:10.146 --> 02:53:11.646
[Scoresby screams]

02:53:16.021 --> 02:53:17.521
[screaming]

02:53:30.979 --> 02:53:32.146
[alarms blaring]

02:53:32.229 --> 02:53:33.437
[adjutant] General,

02:53:37.687 --> 02:53:38.687
Abandon ship.

02:53:40.062 --> 02:53:41.271
Abandon ship!

02:53:41.354 --> 02:53:43.062
[alarm blaring]

02:53:44.271 --> 02:53:45.271
[Lo'ak breathes heavily]

02:53:47.104 --> 02:53:48.146
Stay close.

02:53:59.271 --> 02:54:00.271
Stay close.

02:54:02.729 --> 02:54:03.729
Clear.

02:54:04.896 --> 02:54:05.896
Clear.

02:54:07.521 --> 02:54:09.271
[gunfire in distance]

02:54:11.354 --> 02:54:12.729
[Jake] Tuck in.

02:54:14.937 --> 02:54:15.771
Run!

02:54:15.854 --> 02:54:17.229
[Varang speaking Na'vi]

02:54:27.396 --> 02:54:28.229
Get eyes on me.

02:54:33.187 --> 02:54:34.187
Go, go.

02:54:36.104 --> 02:54:38.062
[grunts, breathing heavily]

02:54:38.146 --> 02:54:39.812
[gunfire]

02:54:48.896 --> 02:54:49.896
I'm here.

02:54:49.979 --> 02:54:51.146
Don't kill them.

02:54:54.187 --> 02:54:55.229
Where are you, boy?

02:54:55.729 --> 02:54:56.854
<c.s0>Step out now.

02:54:57.771 --> 02:54:58.896
[ship crew member screams]

02:55:01.354 --> 02:55:02.771
[Varang chanting in Na'vi]

02:55:06.937 --> 02:55:07.937
[grunts]

02:55:13.396 --> 02:55:14.437
[Quaritch] Spider!

02:55:14.521 --> 02:55:15.729
Do you hear me?

02:55:15.812 --> 02:55:17.271
We're running out of time.

02:55:22.146 --> 02:55:24.146
[chanting in Na'vi continues]

02:55:25.854 --> 02:55:26.687
[whispers] Come on.

02:55:32.062 --> 02:55:33.104
[Mangkwan] <c.s0>Tsahìk.

02:55:42.437 --> 02:55:43.812
I'm here to make a deal.

02:55:44.812 --> 02:55:45.812
Me for them.

02:55:46.521 --> 02:55:47.729
[Quaritch] That can happen.

02:55:48.854 --> 02:55:50.396
Come with me, Son.

02:55:50.479 --> 02:55:51.979
I'm a man of my word.

02:55:54.604 --> 02:55:55.854
Everybody goes home.

02:56:05.604 --> 02:56:06.729
Circle up.

02:56:06.812 --> 02:56:07.812
We're out of here.

02:56:07.896 --> 02:56:09.146
[breathes deeply]

02:56:09.229 --> 02:56:10.521
[♪ tense music plays]

02:56:11.521 --> 02:56:12.646
[grunting]

02:56:26.271 --> 02:56:27.521
[shouts]

02:56:30.271 --> 02:56:31.104
[grunts] Tuk.

02:56:31.187 --> 02:56:32.396
[exclaims]

02:56:32.479 --> 02:56:34.187
[both grunting]

02:56:37.729 --> 02:56:39.104
Come on, Tuk.

02:56:45.437 --> 02:56:46.687
[shouts]

02:56:47.937 --> 02:56:49.521
[shouts]

02:56:50.271 --> 02:56:51.979
[groans]

02:56:59.479 --> 02:57:00.979
[panting]

02:57:02.937 --> 02:57:04.146
Bitch!

02:57:06.937 --> 02:57:08.812
[panting]

02:57:14.854 --> 02:57:15.979
[pants]

02:57:16.604 --> 02:57:18.021
[panting]

02:57:19.979 --> 02:57:21.396
[roars]

02:57:23.146 --> 02:57:23.979
[grunts]

02:57:30.937 --> 02:57:31.937
Go find your mother.

02:57:35.062 --> 02:57:35.896
[whoops]

02:57:36.937 --> 02:57:38.062
[grunting]

02:57:38.604 --> 02:57:39.937
[whooping]

02:57:40.854 --> 02:57:43.062
[grunts, panting]

02:57:50.854 --> 02:57:52.062
Hang on, kid.

02:57:56.562 --> 02:57:58.437
[breathing heavily]

02:58:04.271 --> 02:58:05.271
[shrieks]

02:58:06.812 --> 02:58:09.187
[both grunting]

02:58:09.687 --> 02:58:10.937
Spider, here.

02:58:11.021 --> 02:58:12.229
Jake!

02:58:12.312 --> 02:58:13.354
[grunts] Spider.

02:58:14.187 --> 02:58:15.187
[groans]

02:58:17.396 --> 02:58:19.146
[panting, grunts]

02:58:20.646 --> 02:58:21.521
[grunting]

02:58:24.937 --> 02:58:25.896
Jake.

02:58:25.979 --> 02:58:26.979
Spider.

02:58:27.062 --> 02:58:29.396
[exclaims]

02:58:40.312 --> 02:58:41.187
Go, go!

02:58:41.271 --> 02:58:42.271
[whoops]

02:58:54.604 --> 02:58:55.604
[snarls]

02:59:07.396 --> 02:59:08.396
Shit.

02:59:12.562 --> 02:59:13.896
[grunting, gasping]

02:59:16.896 --> 02:59:19.187
[Spider] Jake! Jake!

02:59:20.146 --> 02:59:21.354
[exclaims]

02:59:25.729 --> 02:59:27.437
[grunting]

02:59:30.396 --> 02:59:31.396
[grunts]

02:59:34.979 --> 02:59:35.812
[snarls]

02:59:38.021 --> 02:59:38.937
I'll kill you!

02:59:39.021 --> 02:59:40.312
I swear!

02:59:44.271 --> 02:59:46.229
Do not test me.

02:59:48.854 --> 02:59:49.854
Give me that.

02:59:53.729 --> 02:59:55.562
You little bastard!

02:59:59.604 --> 03:00:00.896
[Quaritch groans]

03:00:00.979 --> 03:00:01.937
Get out of here.

03:00:02.021 --> 03:00:02.979
Go on.

03:00:06.187 --> 03:00:07.437
[groans]

03:00:07.521 --> 03:00:09.396
[panting, grunts]

03:00:11.062 --> 03:00:12.562
[both grunting]

03:00:26.896 --> 03:00:28.146
[strains]

03:00:53.437 --> 03:00:55.271
[both grunting]

03:01:18.021 --> 03:01:19.021
Oh, shit.

03:01:22.187 --> 03:01:23.687
