03:01:55.437 --> 03:01:56.437
Hand him up.

03:01:56.521 --> 03:01:57.521
Come on.

03:01:58.812 --> 03:02:01.229
[all straining]

03:02:02.396 --> 03:02:03.729
Pull me up.

03:02:10.687 --> 03:02:12.229
[snarls]

03:02:12.812 --> 03:02:14.021
