03:02:14.604 --> 03:02:15.771
Then do it,

03:02:16.604 --> 03:02:17.604
Dad.

03:02:21.562 --> 03:02:22.771
Pull us up.

03:02:46.646 --> 03:02:47.771
Take my hand.

03:02:49.646 --> 03:02:51.312
[all grunting]

03:02:55.062 --> 03:02:56.062
Jake.

03:02:56.562 --> 03:02:57.604
[Jake] Come on.

03:02:58.979 --> 03:02:59.979
We got you.

03:03:00.521 --> 03:03:01.521
We got you.

03:03:01.604 --> 03:03:04.062
[all panting]

03:03:04.896 --> 03:03:05.896
[Jake groans]

03:03:06.646 --> 03:03:08.021
