03:03:27.396 --> 03:03:28.479
We all gonna

03:03:29.312 --> 03:03:31.229
hold hands and sing?

03:03:32.437 --> 03:03:33.896
I "learn to See"?

03:03:36.562 --> 03:03:38.104
You have a choice.

03:03:40.937 --> 03:03:42.646
[ikran shrieks]

03:03:58.354 --> 03:03:59.562
