03:04:05.521 --> 03:04:06.521
[snarls]

03:04:17.479 --> 03:04:19.229
[screams]

03:04:29.896 --> 03:04:31.604
<c.s0>Ma Jake,

03:04:31.687 --> 03:04:32.604
Come here. [sighs]

03:04:32.687 --> 03:04:33.729
[sighs]

03:04:33.812 --> 03:04:35.479
