03:04:55.104 --> 03:04:57.812
[tulkun whistling, rumbling]

03:05:02.687 --> 03:05:03.687
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>We all connect

03:05:03.771 --> 03:05:05.104
<c.s0>with the Great Mother...

03:05:07.354 --> 03:05:08.771
