03:05:28.729 --> 03:05:30.646
[Lo'ak] <c.s0>He was accepted
by the clan.

03:05:44.854 --> 03:05:46.437
<c.s0>In the Spirit World,

03:05:46.521 --> 03:05:49.146
<c.s0>we call upon the strength
of the ancestors.

03:05:51.896 --> 03:05:54.146
