03:06:28.979 --> 03:06:30.229
Sir.

03:06:31.729 --> 03:06:32.896
I See you.

03:06:32.979 --> 03:06:33.979
I See you.

03:06:37.062 --> 03:06:38.062
<c.s0>Skxawng

03:06:39.729 --> 03:06:40.562
